            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "地產｜二手樓價指數連升五周後斷纜",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"地產｜二手樓價指數連升五周後斷纜\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">地產｜二手樓價指數連升五周後斷纜</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本港二手樓價指數連升五周後回軟，反映主要大型屋苑二手住宅樓市走勢的中原城市領先指數(CCL)最新報149.36點，按周輕微下跌0.03%，指數仍連續四周企穩149點以上。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中原地產研究部高級聯席董事楊明儀指出，近日中東局勢惡化，股市波動，但並未阻礙樓市進入新春後傳統季節性旺市，二手成交增多，而且多個新盤準備開售，相信樓價繼續向升。CCL目標156點水平(即2023年通關前的低位)，現時相差6.64點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6ac7f2ee-23d0-3452-a17b-ac5c347ff4a0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中原城市大型屋苑領先指數CCL Mass報150.47點，按周跌0.13%；CCL中小型單位指數報149.31點，按周跌0.02%。兩項指數齊升五周後輕微回軟，同樣為2023年12月初後117周(逾2年)次高。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">CCL大型單位指數報149.6點，按周跌0.09%，連跌兩周共0.19%，仍為2024年5月初後95周(近2年)第3高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">四區樓價連續兩周一升三跌。港島CCL Mass報148.41點，按周跌1.55%，結束兩周連升，仍為2024年4月中後98周(近2年)次高；新界東CCL Mass報158.62點，按周跌0.5%，連跌三周共1.03%，仍為2024年4月底後96周(近2年)第8高；九龍CCL Mass報151.03點，按周跌0.1%，連跌兩周共0.13%，仍為2023年9月中後128周(近2年半)第三高；新界西CCL Mass報136.86點，按周升1.66%，創2024年1月初後112周(逾2年)新高。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2-%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E9%80%A3%E5%8D%87%E4%BA%94%E5%91%A8%E5%BE%8C%E6%96%B7%E7%BA%9C-094944480.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-06 18:03:19",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "本地｜2名找換店顧客攜千萬元於上環遇劫 警埋伏當場拘3人",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"本地｜2名找換店顧客攜千萬元於上環遇劫 警埋伏當場拘3人\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nvJ6N1NDpC3.YMtrx76erg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">本地｜2名找換店顧客攜千萬元於上環遇劫 警埋伏當場拘3人</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上環德輔道中今早發生劫案，2名找換店顧客攜千萬港元在上環站遇劫，探員當場制服3名匪徒。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科警司盧嘉晉表示，警方較早前接獲線報，得悉有犯罪集團會進行搶劫，經警方部署，今天上午約9時在上環地鐵站內採取行動，以串謀行劫拘捕3名男子，年齡介乎19至31歲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2受害人為澳門及香港居民 無財物損失</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">調查顯示，案中2名受害人分別為澳門及香港居民，為親戚關係。今天上午，二人攜帶總值約港幣1000萬元的外幣前往上環一帶找換店兌換港幣，於上環希利街一間找換店成功兌換港幣後，在上環地鐵站內被2名匪徒持刀行劫，當時在場埋伏的警員當場制服2名涉案的匪徒，2名受害人並沒有受到任何的財物損失。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d5c85f90-29e6-32f1-9c54-886b7524e56d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">案發期間，受害人一度與1名匪徒糾纏，左手輕傷，現時情況穩定，在瑪麗醫院接受治療，另1名受害人並沒有受傷，警方在現場亦截獲一輛與案有關的私家車，並拘捕車上1名男司機，3名被捕人士現正被警方扣留調查。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">警方重申，持械行劫是一種非常嚴重的罪行，警方必定會調配最大資源，全力打擊相關罪行，務必把所有犯罪分子繩之於法，維持香港治安。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0-2%E5%90%8D%E6%89%BE%E6%8F%9B%E5%BA%97%E9%A1%A7%E5%AE%A2%E6%94%9C%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%8A%E7%92%B0%E9%81%87%E5%8A%AB-%E8%AD%A6%E5%9F%8B%E4%BC%8F%E7%95%B6%E5%A0%B4%E6%8B%983%E4%BA%BA-090217291.html",
